sequenceDiagram
   participant Student
   participant FocusTimeSystem
   participant SyncService
   participant CloudServer


   FocusTimeSystem->>SyncService: Initiate Data Sync
   activate FocusTimeSystem
   activate SyncService
   SyncService->>CloudServer: Send Session Data
   activate CloudServer
   CloudServer--x SyncService: Network Error
   deactivate CloudServer
   SyncService-->>FocusTimeSystem: Notify Sync Failure
   deactivate SyncService
   FocusTimeSystem-->>Student: Display Error Message
   FocusTimeSystem->>FocusTimeSystem: Save Data Locally for Retry
   deactivate FocusTimeSystem
